== Ubuzima bwe bwite ==
Antoinette Niyongira yavukiye mu karere ka Kamonyi akaba ari umufasha wa Patrick Kigenza aho bakoze ubukwe 2015.<ref>https://hose.rw/antoinette-niyongira-atwite-umwana-wa-kabiri-amafoto/</ref> ntago yigeze ahakurira kuko amashuri abanza yayasoreje mu mujyi wa [[Kigali]] mbere yuko ajya kwiga icyiciro rusange cy'amashuri yisumbuye i kabgayi muri St Joseph yasoreje amashuri yisumbuye muri Groupe Scholaire de Rulindo mu 2011 aho yize bitewe n'amanota yari yabonye yahawe kujya kwiga muri KIE agakurikirana ubwarimu, ubwo abandi bajyaga mw'itorero we ntiyashije kujyayo kubera yari arwaye ibi byatumye amaze koroherwa atekereza akantu yakora bagenzi be bakazasanga hari aho ageze.<ref>https://igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/ibyo-wamenya-ku-rugendo-rwa-antoinette-niyongira-umunyamakuru-uri-mu-bagezweho</ref>  

