== Umwuga ==
Antoinette Niyongira amaze imyaka icumi mw'itangazamakuru yanyuze kubinyamakuru binyuranye aho yanyuze kuri radiyo isango Star kuri radiyo 10 ubu akaba akor akuri KISS FM aho yagiyeyo muri 2015.<ref>https://umuryango.rw/index.php?page=print&id_article=57414</ref> akaba anafite umuyoboro wa yutube(Youtube) agaragazaho amashusho yigisha guteka yatangiye shyiraho amashusho ari guteka ibiryo bitandukanye ariko ibyinshi bikaba ibitetse kuburyo butamenyerewe, Ingero nkaho ashobora gutekesha inyama inzoga, inkoko akayitekesha ubuki n'ibindi bitandukanye,<ref>https://igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/ndi-umuhanga-mu-gutekesha-inkoko-ubuki-antoinette-niyongira-yinjiye-mubyo</ref>Antoinette Niyongira amenyerewe mukiganiro MID DAY gica kuri KISS FM.<ref>https://yegob.rw/abanyamakurukazi-babica-bigacika-mu-rwanda-kubera-kugira-amajwi-yahogoje-benshiamafoto/</ref>

